cker.\n2. **Batch API calls**: Currently appears to fetch each ticker individually. Combine into single WebSocket or batched REST call.\n3. **Virtualise the table** (react-window or tanstack-virtual) — already slow with only 10 rows, will choke at 100+.\n4. **Cache RSI/Rebound calculations** client-side using a Map keyed by ticker+minute. Recalculate only on new candle close.\n5. **Move momentum calculation** to Web Worker to prevent UI jank on live updates.\n\n**Priority order**: Fix the 2026 date bug immediately → add sorting + color coding → implement virtualisation.", "data_timeframe": "🔴 LIVE INTRA-DAY (1-minute candles) • Last price: 05:11 02 Apr 2026"}
